  "texts": [
    "Firstly, it is important to acknowledge the remarkable appeal of this work as a choice for personal reading at home.",
    "This work effectively combines the qualities that make it an excellent resource for addressing traditional issues in the subject of \"home reading\": it captivates students' interest, stimulates literary discussions, and also serves as a valuable resource for learning English phraseology.A statistical analysis was conducted to support our selection of the novel Theatre by W.S.",
    "Maugham as the \"action movie\" that can effectively improve the students' phraseologically deficient speech.",
    "Initially, the overall count of phraseological units in the complete novel Theatre was determined to be approximately 550.",
    "This count was based on the novel's 270 pages and 29 chapters."
